The paper deals with sketching techniques for quadratic forms, which involves topics such as linear algebra, graph Laplacians, and spectral sparsification. This suggests that the paper may belong to categories such as cs.DS (data structures and algorithms), cs.CG (computational geometry), and cs.IT (information theory).
